<tr valign="top" height="400" >
<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" style="font-size: 12pt;">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><font face="arial">Thank you for getting in touch with Kingsbridge.</font><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><font face="arial">Because we operate the Direct Debits payment schedule over 10 months for your 12-month policy duration,&nbsp;</font><b style="font-size: 12pt;">we’re happy to confirm that all the payments for your policy have been made</b><font face="arial">. To honour your cancellation request, please rest assured that&nbsp;</font><u style="font-size: 12pt;">your policy has now been removed from auto-renewal</u><font face="arial">&nbsp;and no further payments will be taken.</font><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">To confirm,&nbsp;</span><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">your policy will be active for the period (DDMMYYYY to DDMMYYYY)</b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><font face="arial">If you still&nbsp;</font><u style="font-size: 12pt;">wish to proceed with your cancellation, please carefully review the information below and confirm by replying to this email within 7 calendar days</u><font face="arial">.&nbsp;<br></font><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br><b>Important information regarding your insurance cover</b><br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">IR35 Protect operates on a ‘claims made’ basis, so the policy must be active to respond to most claims. However, for&nbsp;<a href="https://www.kingsbridge.co.uk/policy-documents/">sections 10-12</a>&nbsp;on your policy there is a 4-year extended reporting period for you to notify us of a claim for an investigation during the period your policy was active. Any claim in these sections must be notified to insurers within 30 days of an insured event taking place and before any response to HMRC. Your appointed representation will work with you to respond and manage communications with HMRC.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Whether you’re currently insured with Kingsbridge or not, our customer service team is always here to help. Please don’t hesitate to reply to this email if you need any further information on any of the above.<br></span><font face="arial" style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Customer Service Team<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>E:&nbsp;</span><a href="mailto:customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk" style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk</a><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>